column5: Well i just wanted to take this few minutes i have before heading into work and wish each and everyone of you a very merry christmas and a happy & Prosperous new year.    STAY safe everyone have fun and remember DON'T drink & drive.
Merry Christmass back at ya... and yes... no drinking and a driving... drink all ya want... but cab it!!!
